   |  |  |     |     |     |
   |__|  |_____|     |_____|
   +--------------------------------------->
                                          t
   ^
 /Q|                           (!)
   |__    _____       _____    __
   |  |  |     |     |     |  |  |
   |  |  |     |     |     |  |  |
   |  |__|     |_____|     |__|  |______
   +--------------------------------------->
                                          t



@endnode

